係cancer，就再食返，之後就一直食到依家，覺得突然改變生活習慣都係易出事，最多食淡d（已經食到最淡）<br />\n<br />\n可以留個tg黎傾下，唔好自己嚇自己"},{"pid":"11599c8321a70f9720f5a716f0ca9f4e685ab35c","tid":2252391,"uid":11578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"又話買保險冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17f82d92deedcddedbccea2ea7e513ebf4412b4","tid":2252391,"uid":37538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"話俾你聽係樓下診所十年前check完有乙肝但買保險嗰時冇報，保險公司一樣check到<br />\n照樓主講法，保險佬去醫院icu sell單應該屈左機"},{"pid":"6a619487baf91531c777265e9cfbe924e462c00c","tid":2252391,"uid":167566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"我決定先買保險 捱一年睇下點<br />\n<br />\n如果係無事 係可以唔理<br />\n<br />\n有事既話我都攪唔店 <br />\n<br />\n下一年我會好好注意自己健康<br />\n<br />\n落力儲錢<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165fb16d8361154949e6a61642be5cab324bdba5","tid":2252391,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a619487baf91531c777265e9cfbe924e462c00c","tid":2252391,"uid":167566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"我決定先買保險 捱一年睇下點<br />\n<br />\n如果係無事 係可以唔理<br />\n<br />\n有事既話我都攪唔店 <br />\n<br />\n下一年我會好好注意自己健康<br />\n<br />\n落力儲錢<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"你claim保險張claim form醫生要填<br />\n張form會唔會寫幾時發現個問題就唔知啦"},{"pid":"76fb67aa65b09c570db0cec6274152f08b73183c","tid":2252391,"uid":63549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b046a4fde891528515fa32775e4ab7e18ae8c1e5","tid":2252391,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbccbfee133803ca1bf29fd1eac693656b62aa13","tid":2252391,"uid":182693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"公司有冇醫療保險<br />\n<br />\n自購保險未必有<br />\n有sign &amp; symptoms 未必係確診都已經唔會保障<br